The PEAR::HTML_Table package provides methods
for easy and efficient design of HTML tables.
- Lots of customization options.
- Tables can be modified at any time.
- The logic is the same as standard HTML
editors.
- Handles col and rowspans.
- PHP code is shorter, easier to read and to
maintain.
- Tables options can be reused.
